Textbook 28.4.4

Problem 4. Use override.aes to make the legend on the following plot easier to see.

ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price)) +
  geom_point(aes(colour = cut), alpha = 1/20)

.

ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price)) +
  geom_point(aes(colour = cut), alpha = 1/20) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(override.aes = list(alpha = 1)))
